{"tid":325180,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[食糊] 有冇人都好鍾意食中式糖水？","createTime":"2017-07-17T04:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T13:44:32.000Z","uid":34701,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e51552cb7e12ca3b3b87be34c1f500f1f52660bd","tid":325180,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"芝麻糊，核桃糊，杏仁露，腰果露，腐竹蛋，薑汁撞奶，雙皮奶呢啲全部都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋一定要熱食，香好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇同好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef08cecf020248d1e2e8715a3e5b3bb2b389f94b","tid":325180,"uid":119783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T04:46:32.000Z","msg":"芝麻糊正阿屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔好太甜"},{"pid":"a9b2e15fde6b93b053245646276d18651b5fd3ca","tid":325180,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T04:54:51.000Z","msg":"我係生果派 應該係西式定中式"},{"pid":"d6065a419097e58fa37c8c65a21f9a2952454014","tid":325180,"uid":34701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T04:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係生果派 應該係西式定中式</blockquote><br />\n中式好少用生果，用豆類同果仁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生果嘅話淨係諗到木瓜雪耳糖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520dbd52df9a32aec65b0a9aec0ed7da8ed8c0d0","tid":325180,"uid":34701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:00:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>芝麻糊正阿屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔好太甜</blockquote><br />\n太甜多數開粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我鍾意食即磨，多數去啲老字號會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9232df8d3b793b5279a5dbd3bd7934382cda525","tid":325180,"uid":89362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl