:325180,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老母煲咩都會加薑<br />\n加薑加太多簡直係垃圾<br />\n唔係哂嘢嘅話我一定係佢面前倒咗佢</blockquote><br />\n你話驚燥得濟叫佢落少啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該得蕃薯糖水先會落薑啫，其他嗰啲糊都唔啱味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蕃薯糖水多薑, 仲有湯丸個片糖水加好多薑先好味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多薑正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e052c16f1e05ba59a9ab7fa34f4384962b30184","tid":325180,"uid":8557,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:53:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全部唔入流<br />\n<br />\n桑寄生蓮子蛋茶先係中式糖水之王</blockquote><br />\n會唔會你果碗先唔入流呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21c64507d1df862b76a544e2123721df75db14d","tid":325180,"uid":27324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:18:24.000Z","msg":"九龍城 地茂館 合成糖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58d6c2908f516f5957b4a6ac4714ff35a25474b","tid":325180,"uid":76679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"完全唔食西式糖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c943df744b9954debc697846cc25f50b16a3fd6","tid":325180,"uid":7020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:34:13.000Z","msg":"腐竹白果 紅豆沙 紫米露 番薯糖水<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3c8331c5bfb7cd9d14ed779c6fcfe7a8a1288b","tid":325180,"uid":19858,"like":0,"disl